---
title: Chicken, Cheesy Spinach & Mushroom Soup  with Pearl Pasta, Cannellini Beans & Chili Flakes
description: Is there anything cozier than a hearty bowl of soup? We think not, which is why our chefs created this soul-warming Italian-inspired meal. Tender white beans simmer with earthy mushrooms, spinach, and lots of garlic, plus tender, springy fun-to-eat pearl pasta in a rich veggie broth. Ladle the soup into bowls and sprinkle generously with our Italian cheese blend  for a meltingly delicious topper, then finish with as many spicy red pepper flakes as you’d like.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/669ed827f2f831ddecf68216-36f417a2.jpeg
